---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy -- 24K Labs" description="Privacy policy for 24K Labs. Short, honest, and actually readable.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header__glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <span class="page-header__badge">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-header__desc">
        What we collect, what we don't, and why you should actually read this one.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose reveal">

        <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> April 9, 2026</p>

        <h2>What We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Request metadata: timestamps, service type, tokens consumed</li>
          <li>IP address (for rate limiting only)</li>
          <li>Payment transaction hashes (x402) or Stripe payment IDs</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>We don't create user accounts.</li>
          <li>We don't store your submitted code permanently.</li>
          <li>We don't track you across sessions.</li>
          <li>We don't sell data. To anyone. Ever.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Code Processing</h2>
        <p>
          Your code is sent to Anthropic's Claude API for analysis. See
          <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/policies" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Anthropic's privacy policy</a>
          for how they handle API inputs. We do not train models on your code.
          Anthropic's API data retention policies apply to data in transit through their systems.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We don't use cookies. The site is static. No tracking pixels, no analytics scripts.
          When we add analytics in the future, we'll update this policy and it'll be
          something privacy-respecting.
        </p>

        <h2>Third Parties</h2>
        <p>Here's the complete list of third parties that touch your data:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Anthropic</strong> -- Claude API for code analysis</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> -- CDN and DNS</li>
          <li><strong>Railway</strong> -- API hosting</li>
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong> -- Payment processing (coming soon)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>That's it. No ad networks, no data brokers, no "partners."</p>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          Request logs are retained for <strong>90 days</strong> for debugging and billing
          reconciliation, then deleted. We don't keep data longer than we need it.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Want us to delete any data associated with your transactions? Email
          <a href="mailto:sean@24klabs.ai">sean@24klabs.ai</a> and we'll handle it.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about privacy? Email
          <a href="mailto:sean@24klabs.ai">sean@24klabs.ai</a>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
